snippet.title: BEST CHOCOLATE - The Highest Rated Chocolate Bar in the World
snippet.description:
In this video, I show you what the best chocolate bars are and the countries they come from! I hope you learned something about chocolate, I know I did!

The text in the video may be hard to see, so here is a list of the best chocolate in the world:
                                    company                                   origin_name rating
1                                     Amedei                                         Chuao   5.00
2                                     Amedei                                 Toscano Black   5.00
3                                   A. Morin                                       Pablino   4.00
4                                   A. Morin                                         Chuao   4.00
5                                   A. Morin                          Chanchamayo Province   4.00
6                                      Amano                                        Morobe   4.00
7                                      Amano                                        Guayas   4.00
8                                     Amedei                                     Porcelana   4.00
9                                     Amedei                                          Nine   4.00
10                                    Amedei                                    Madagascar   4.00
11                                    Amedei                                 Toscano Black   4.00
12                                      AMMA             Monte Alegre, 3 diff. plantations   4.00
13                                     Arete                         Coto Brus, Terciopelo   4.00
14                                     Arete                                       Phantom   4.00
15                                     Arete                                         Chuno   4.00
16                       Artisan du Chocolat                                         Haiti   4.00
17                           Bar Au Chocolat                                Maranon Canyon   4.00
18                             Benoit Nihant                                 Rio Peripa H.   4.00
19                             Benoit Nihant      Bali, Sukrama Bros. Farm, Melaya, 62hr C   4.00
20                        Beschle (Felchlin)                                       Ecuador   4.00
21                                    Bonnat                                         Kaori   4.00
22                                    Bonnat                                         Haiti   4.00
23                                    Bonnat                      Madagascar, 100% criollo   4.00
24                                    Bonnat                          Porcelana, Venezuela   4.00
25                                    Bonnat                       Ocumare, Puerto Cabello   4.00

Not in the list? Let me know, what do you think the best chocolate is? 

Data: https://www.kaggle.com/rtatman/chocolate-bar-ratings
Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X8yPK1Q_IiI

If you want more of these videos, let me know by leaving a like and subscribing!
